OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 2 Jul to Sat 11 JulFA
OL,6,Fdrier start to July for most. Cloudier
OL,7,Ftowards the west, otherwise a good
OL,8,Fdeal of sunshine for most. Some
OL,9,Fnorthwestern parts may still see rain
OL,10,Fon occasion, perhaps accompanied by
OL,11,Fstrong winds at times. Temperatures
OL,12,Fare likely to start off near average
OL,13,Fin the north and slightly warmer than
OL,14,Faverage in the south, but fairly
OL,15,Fwidely tending to increase further as
OL,16,Fhigh pressure dominates the weather
OL,17,Finto the second week of July,
OL,18,Fespecially across England and Wales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
